definitions.definition: Having a physical, tangible body; material , corporeal .
Of or pertaining to the body, especially the human body; bodily .
Pertaining to the body (the thorax and abdomen ), as distinguished from the head , limbs and wings , etc.

main_definition: ( archaic ) Having a physical, tangible body; material , corporeal .
secondary_definitions: Of or pertaining to the body, especially the human body; bodily .
( zoology ) Pertaining to the body (the thorax and abdomen ), as distinguished from the head , limbs and wings , etc.
